      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHICO CASINO (1) gets the nod in an ordinary BM58. Raced handy but struggled to quicken in heavy going last start over 1000m at Orange. Races well here with a couple of wins and a placing from six visits. At peak fitness and on his best form would be too good for these. CHEAP SHOT (4) wound up late to finish a close fifth under 61.5kgs when resuming over 1000m at Orange last time out. Up in class but strips fitter, drops 4kgs, and has a strong record at today's journey. Looms as a definite threat. MISS CAPRICORN (2) opened this prep with a couple of fine efforts then laboured in heavy going last time. Handy mare who can return to form on firmer footing. KOBOLD (5) started at $8.00 first-up last time out when he failed to finish. Subsequent trial winner who should be ready to run well. JACOB JOE (8) is very fit and from a nice draw can sneak into the frame.",
